{
  "id": "adv_event_2510_01_03",
  "title": "出し物考案中",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――後日、星見プロ東京寮にて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "endTime": 1.5333334089,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yuu Suzumura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_03-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "うーん、オリジナルの劇……プカミちゃん……\nうわぁぁ、あかん！　すぐ『ぷりエン』に引っ張られる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.5000000756,
      "endTime": 14.117233161200001,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 11933.3332577
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_03-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "あれ、優ちゃんまた脚本書いてるんだ。『劇団★見』\nの次回作？　不思議の国のアリス大好評だったもんね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.3333334089,
      "endTime": 24.1333334089,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yuu Suzumura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_03-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "今回は再来週学園祭で生徒会がするミュージカルの\n脚本なんよ。せやけどなーんかうまいこといかんくてな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.3333334089,
      "endTime": 34.1166631818,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_03-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "そうだったんだ\n準備、大変だよね……何に悩んでたの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.3333298485,
      "endTime": 40.9000005086,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yuu Suzumura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_03-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "この間うちらがやった『ぷりてぃーエンジェル』の舞台\nを学園祭で見たいって声が生徒達から沢山あがってて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.13333112,
      "endTime": 50.1681610227,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yuu Suzumura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_03-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "さすがに権利の問題でそれは出来んから\nオリジナルのストーリーを考えてるんやけど難しくてな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.3666644533,
      "endTime": 58.708342882,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yuu Suzumura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_03-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "『ぷりエン』ぽいけど『ぷりエン』ではないオリジ\nナリティのある戦う女の子の話を描きたいんやけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.8999977867,
      "endTime": 66.8666642944,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_03-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "バトルものだよね……うーん……あ、最近千紗ちゃんに\nオススメしてもらった映画はバトルものだったよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.0666644533,
      "endTime": 77.2549434145,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_03-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "参考になるか分かんないけど、神様に仕える聖なる\nシスターさん達が悪魔を祓って人々を救うお話で……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.4666664879,
      "endTime": 86.09485271380001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yuu Suzumura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_03-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "シスター！？　めっちゃええな！\n戦うシスターなんて舞台上での衣装映えもええやろし！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.2000059248,
      "endTime": 93.7416884542,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yuu Suzumura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_03-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "それに絶対、瑠依ちゃんに似合うやん……！\nもう絶対可愛い……ああ、うちを祓ってほしい……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.9333438357,
      "endTime": 104.46590590080001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_03-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "分かるよ！　もし琴乃ちゃんがシスターになったら\n私も祓われたいって思うもん！　うへへ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.6666771691,
      "endTime": 112.26336667950001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yuu Suzumura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_03-yu008.m4a",
      "text": "よし、うちと瑠依ちゃんが戦うシスターになる物語で\n決まりや！　ほんまおおきにな、渚ちゃん！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.4666771691,
      "endTime": 120.83388832019999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_studentcouncilroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "seitokai",
      "startTime": 122.0833438357
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_03-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "はあ……それでシスターの話になったのね\n一言ぐらい相談してくれても良かったのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.1333438357,
      "endTime": 131.4770631274,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_studentcouncilroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "seitokai",
      "startTime": 131.6887408694
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yuu Suzumura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_03-yu009.m4a",
      "text": "はっ！　ごめんな、締め切りが近くて焦ってもうた……\nい、勢いで衣装の発注まで昨晩済ませてもうてて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.6887408694,
      "endTime": 142.45900816530002,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 19044.593735500002
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_studentcouncilroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "seitokai",
      "startTime": 142.6554024499
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_03-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "し、仕事が速いわね……でも別にいいわよ\nとりあえず時間もないし読み合わせをしましょうか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.6554024499,
      "endTime": 151.0354023736,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 8677.932154999979
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_studentcouncilroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "seitokai",
      "startTime": 147.6333346049
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_studentcouncilroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "seitokai",
      "startTime": 151.2470801156
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi Igawa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_03-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "おーい、二人とも。お取込み中悪いね。ちょっと\nいいかな？　生徒会に解決してほしい問題があってさ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 151.2470801156,
      "endTime": 159.8518648903,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_studentcouncilroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "seitokai",
      "startTime": 160.0470801156
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yuu Suzumura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_03-yu010.m4a",
      "text": "葵ちゃん！？　これまためずらしいお客さんやなぁ\nとりあえずお話聞かせて下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 160.0470801156,
      "endTime": 167.5019215387,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_studentcouncilroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "seitokai",
      "startTime": 164.9333346049
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_studentcouncilroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "seitokai",
      "startTime": 167.7137355925
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi Igawa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_03-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "僕達のクラスはお化け屋敷をすることになったんだけど\nお化け役の子が全く怖くなくて困っててさ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 167.7137355925,
      "endTime": 176.641876042,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi Igawa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_03-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "一人だけならまだしも、全員なんだか可愛くてね\nどうすれば迫力が出せるか意見が聞きたいんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 176.8470689258,
      "endTime": 185.44767565339998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_studentcouncilroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "seitokai",
      "startTime": 185.6470638396
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yuu Suzumura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_03-yu012.m4a",
      "text": "ちょい試しにうちがやってみよか\nひゅ～どろどろ、うらめしや～、呪っちゃうぞ～……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 185.6470638396,
      "endTime": 196.8546375396,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_studentcouncilroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "seitokai",
      "startTime": 188.4000012715
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_studentcouncilroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "seitokai",
      "startTime": 197.0470638396
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_03-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "全然可愛いわね……もっとこう背筋が凍るような\n演技がいいんじゃないかしら。ぐわっ！　みたいな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 197.0470638396,
      "endTime": 206.2637336852,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 16052.937431899976
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_studentcouncilroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "seitokai",
      "startTime": 204.3566679382
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_studentcouncilroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "seitokai",
      "startTime": 206.4754114272
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi Igawa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_03-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど……分かった。ぐわっ！　とやってみるよ\n呪ってやる……お前だけじゃなく、家族、友人、諸共",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 206.4754114272,
      "endTime": 223.480876744,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_studentcouncilroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "seitokai",
      "startTime": 208.5666679382
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
